            "descriptionRaw": "<color=#FFD780FF>Normal Attack</color>\nUses Mehrak to perform up to 4 consecutive attacks.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Charged Attack</color>\nDrains Stamina over time to perform continuous slashes.\nAt the end of the sequence, performs a more powerful slash.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Plunging Attack</color>\nPlunges from mid-air to strike the ground, damaging opponents along the path and dealing AoE DMG upon impact.",
            "name": "Schematic Setup"
        },
