            "descriptionRaw": "Uses Mehrak's mapping ability for offensive purposes, initiating a radial scan that deals <color=#99FF88FF>AoE Dendro DMG</color>. It will also scan all Dendro Cores in its AoE and cause them to immediately burst.\n\n<i>Mehrak was created through the modification of ancient technology and may have some other functions apart from mapping work...</i>",
            "name": "Artistic Ingenuity"
